data.subject: Here`s That Rainy Day (Feat. Stan Getz) (From `Getz Au Go Go`)
data.lyric:
Maybe I should have saved
 Those leftover dreams
 Funny, but here's that rainy day
 Here's that rain

data.subject: Eu E Voce (Me And You) (Feat. Stan Getz) (From `Getz Au Go Go`)
data.lyric:
Podem me chamar
 e me pedir e me rogar
 e podem mesmo falar mal
 
 Ficar de mal, que nao faz mal
 Po

data.subject: Corcovado (Feat. Stan Getz) (From `Getz Au Go Go`)
data.lyric:
Quiet nights of quiet stars
 Quiet chords from my guitar
 Floating on the silence that surrounds us
